## Styling
- Prefer Tailwind utility classes for styling.
- Tailwind content scanning: `./src/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}`.
- PostCSS plugins: `@tailwindcss/postcss`, `autoprefixer`.
- SCSS entry: `src/styles/scss/main.scss` with `@use 'tailwindcss';`.
- Class composition: Use `clsx`; avoid custom helpers.
